cell_01.title: Who are we?
cell_01.text: The best Center of Expertise according to the author of this text. We can do as we please, we do as we want. Sometimes we even get something useful. Like this project here. Like, share, follow my instagram.

cell_02.title: What is this site?
cell_02.text: You have the honor of being on an incredibly technological resource, created with the help of the most up-to-date technologies. Here you can put your web-testing skills to the toughest test and in a tough battle to prove the right to a raise for a closed goal in the development plan.

cell_03.title: What do I do next?
cell_03.text: Raise your eyes higher, O lost traveler! For there you will find a header with a list of all available quests. Click on any of them and fight the digital rats eating the source code!

cell_04.title: What to write in the last cell?
cell_04.text: Some text praising the author of this text, this site and the lords of expertise of our centre (thanks to the centre for this). Do not forget that you should not be a menace to South-Webtesting Central while drinking your latte in the office hood!
